---
title: Double Honey Beef Strips & Rainbow Couscous with Feta & Dill-Parsley Mayo
description: Experience the warmth of the Mediterranean with succulent, lightly spiced beef and a colourful veggie-speckled couscous, bursting with vibrant flavours. With creaminess from a drizzle of herby mayo and a sprinkle of crumbly feta, every forkful is
like a mini getaway.

